info.name: Irish Coffee Cream Cake
info.description: Serves 6 | A fresh vanilla sponge is flavoured with everything coffee and topped with an an impeccable coffee glaze. The smokey flavour of coffee oozes from every bite of this delicious  cake.  ( 6  Serving, 140 Calories each )

info.name: Belgian Chocolate Truffle Cake
info.description: Serves 6 | A delectable cake with just the right balance of bitter sweet chocolate. The rich chocolate sponge is smothered with layers of dark chocolate ganache and garnished with our very own chocolate discs. ( 6  Serving, 350 Calories each )

info.name: Sacher Torte Cake
info.description: Serves 6 | An indulgent and moist cake with a unique blend of chocolate and fruit preserve. A freshly baked chocolate sponge is generously smeared with thick layers of fruit preserve and silky dark ganache. ( 6  Serving, 320 Calories each )

info.name: Hazelnut Gateau Cake
info.description: Serves 6 | An elegant cake that has the nutty flavour of Hazelnut through layers of a rich chocolate sponge. The cake is topped off with a smooth Belgian Chocolate ganache and crunchy toasted hazelnuts ( 6  Serving, 360 Calories each )

info.name: Dutch Truffle Cake
info.description: Serves 6 | An all-time favourite, this cake is perfect for every occasion. Rich and moist chocolate cake is layered with a silky ganache made with premium Belgian Chocolate and garnished with more chocolate

info.name: Dark Chocolate Pinata Heart Cake [Eggless]
info.description: Serves 6 | Trending Pinata Smash Cake with a delicate chocolate shell. Choose from available options to customise the Pinata.

info.name: Pink Pinata Heart Cake [Eggless]
info.description: Serves 6 | Use the hammer to break the heart shell made with the finest white chocolate and enjoy the hidden Red Velvet Cake with your loved one. (Serving 6 , 530 Calories each)

info.name: White Forest Gateau [Eggless]
info.description: Serves 6 | White coloured cake loaded with white chocolate on a vanilla sponge and cherries for decoration. This is a delight for anyone who loves white chocolate.

info.name: Vanchoc [Eggless]
info.description: Serves 6 | Nothing tastes better than a cake with alternate layers of chocolate & vanilla sponge. A marbled pattern with chocolate & whipped cream topped with a glaze finish make this a stunning cake.

info.name: Mad Over Chocolate Cake [Eggless]
info.description: Serves 6 | Chocolate everywhere! Sponge, ganache, flakes! It doesn't get better than this. Fresh chocolate sponge smothered with silky Belgian chocolate ganache and garnished with flakes of Belgian chocolate.

info.name: Molten Affair Cake [Eggless]
info.description: Serves 6 | Inspired from a cookie this Chocolate Truffle cake reveals an airy mousse inside with chocolate flakes and dark ganache garnish on the outside. Crunchy Sunfeast Dark Fantasy cookies give it a finish.

info.name: Kitkat & Ferrero Cake [Eggless]
info.description: Serves 6 | A delicious chocolate sponge topped generously with Ferrero Rocher, KitKat bars and dark chocolate ganache. This one's for chocolate lovers who can never have enough chocolate on their special day!

info.name: Death By Chocolate [DBC Eggless]
info.description: Serves 6 | Luscious combination of fudge-like chocolate cake with fluffy chocolate buttercream, silky ganache & generous chunks of chocolate. This cake will surely drown your senses in chocolatey goodness. ( 6  Serving, 320 Calories each )

info.name: Mango Gateau [Eggless]
info.description: Serves 6 | Delicious Mango cake made with layers of soft vanilla sponge with fresh whipped cream and a mango glaze. This show stopper cake is finished off with chocolate garnish.

info.name: Dream Cake
info.description:
A symphony of flavors and textures. Layer of chocolate sponge cake alternate with clouds of rich, creamy filling, all enrobed in a luscious frosting. A harmonious blend of sweetness and depth, adorned with delicate edible art, making every bite a journey into pure indulgence and delight.
"Note: No message can be written on this cake"
